'''Soul Blazer''' features a magic system where the player collects various soul magics throughout the game. Each magic type has unique properties, costs, and uses.

== Overview ==

Magic in Soul Blazer is acquired by releasing specific souls from monster lairs. Each magic consumes GEMs when used and has different effects ranging from combat spells to utility abilities.

