== Magic Data Structure ==

Each magic entry is 8 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Field !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Power || Base magic power
|-
| $01 || 1 || Element || Element type ($00-$07)
|-
| $02 || 1 || Range || Effect range/distance
|-
| $03 || 1 || Cost || GEM cost to cast
|-
| $04 || 1 || Effect || Effect type ID
|-
| $05 || 1 || Targets || Max targets/behavior
|-
| $06-$07 || 2 || Animation || Animation sequence ID
|}

